{"tid":1588072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有片］中共駐港部隊在營區竟然演練冒充香港警察","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:21:24.000Z","uid":272197,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9439591dbb73c44c99f6f4a030527acf450e841e","tid":1588072,"uid":272197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"Twitter@LIFETIME視界：令人震驚，中共駐港部隊在營區竟然演練冒充香港警察。這反映兩個問題：1）之前香港社會一直懷疑港警中混有中共軍警，越來越接近真相大白。2）可能暴露了中共&ldquo;不出兵&rdquo;的武裝鎮壓香港反送中運動的計劃，即用駐港部隊執行鎮壓任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lifetimeuscn/status/1175577929578962945?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flifetimeuscn%2Fstatus%2F1175577929578962945%3Fs%3D21&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=c0b2dead\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flifetimeuscn%2Fstatus%2F1175577929578962945%3Fs%3D21&h=823b09bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lifetimeuscn/status/1175577929578962945?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n我自己試著做咗一次Fact Check：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jw6FtxK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjw6FtxK.png&h=b4894974&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngJc355.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngJc355.png&h=25c8f47e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJ568xM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJ568xM.png&h=d818437a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdfOCq8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdfOCq8.png&h=632ebff6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8zDfcQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8zDfcQ.png&h=dfa5cb1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fb87135831aba56a4b7e23ce3a6d85ed64c0daf","tid":1588072,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:11:43.000Z",